[normal]Janette Sadik-Khan[bold], who was appointed to the role of Traffic Commissioner in New York City in 2007 reflects on and details the thinking behind successful initiatives to reshape street life in the 5 boroughs, i
[normal]ncluding the addition of pedestrian zones in Times Square and the arrival of Citi Bikes.
